9-96ea-9e5cc09fc8be\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Indodana PayLater","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Indodana PayLater","Slug":"indodana-paylater","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"a213be1d-345e-4205-bcee-8b7eac8b2fa6\"><img data-block-id=\"10d7cc22-f0d0-47d2-94a8-50f1aa4fb80b\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/indodana-logo.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"410\" height=\"67\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:410px;height:67px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"893eb041-ea31-40cf-97da-ba3157c85a93\">Indodana PayLater es un servicio de crédito digital que permite a los usuarios comprar bienes o servicios a crédito en varios comercios asociados con Indodana Finance.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Características</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"549\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:549px;width:549px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:263px;\"><col style=\"width:286px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"402452f7-7a96-45f3-856a-beec3466fb7a\"><strong>Código de canal</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"05407c07-b8af-488b-89d9-cac0f7afe7c1\"><code>INDODANA</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"e924926f-9906-4496-af4a-b319c2a2c8d4\"><strong>Moneda</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"f9fb2471-2b74-46e3-bff9-65c970ccf6f6\">IDR</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"6598736d-d850-48ae-b29e-ba649fb13157\"><strong>Monto mínimo</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"03f04c64-2bea-4ca6-b943-0b19dc761960\">10,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"93c4567d-ddd5-461c-8459-70cc0cce1024\"><strong>Monto máximo</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"94f9ba98-fea6-4616-b214-6249f8570fbd\">25,000,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"73a8ce05-a222-44fb-b6c6-fa9069d5dfc4\"><strong>Flujo de aprobación del usuario</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"b94b9f42-78d6-4d4f-aee3-37135c282d04\">REDIRECT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"4888d640-07c9-4a08-aa89-fd2f705958bd\"><strong>Guardar</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"c76e04ad-3009-4a7c-9571-cc73ccb8d33f\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"d4dd8a87-001f-4750-954f-3b945aba5e48\"><strong>Recurrente</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"b72664bc-4072-4703-8b44-eedc8d7b25b3\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"1a306633-bbbe-4f04-bf87-db43583cea7b\"><strong>Auth &amp; capture</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"505298a6-70eb-4d89-8ffc-88451f0b57ef\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"6dafaffe-056c-47dd-9363-46082a9133f7\"><strong>Captura parcial</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\" style=\"overflow:hidden;padding:2px 3px 2px 3px;vertical-align:bottom;\"><p data-block-id=\"5a4c7842-211c-4be6-a586-a8dd9f77b9b8\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"dce8b2c9-f302-4b39-b28f-1629758eefff\"><strong>Múltiple captura parcial</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"0d93987b-c443-49e2-9e09-d797f5afb92e\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"0cf87f08-cadc-4646-83a5-749b7c38114e\"><strong>Vencimiento de la solicitud de Pago</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"32efc4c6-add5-42da-aa43-7608988a2307\">24 horas</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"87ed7ee5-1a1d-45b0-92d9-7d7737e62cf8\"><strong>Validez del token de Pago</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"0b8edd45-70d1-49d9-aec3-4175e7479f8a\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"ba0dce38-3f3e-49d7-ae0d-da0beca04eb7\"><strong>Tiempo de Liquidación</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"82f5abe4-5a18-4709-95e6-62bc2b1a554e\">T+2 días hábiles</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"94784d78-3f48-4267-bcfa-f5baf2381b19\"><strong>Reembolso</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"d51c60f7-a1f0-44f9-b0cc-b95849842593\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"783f9060-f315-483c-b020-37f8079c7e5f\"><strong>Reembolso parcial</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"c62c20b0-37df-4860-b3d4-3c0006015ca6\">&#x2705;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"55cbaf83-ec18-4147-8950-585e0c4aaba7\"><strong>Múltiple reembolso parcial</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"8daf5e76-f54e-47c3-b243-11502d159866\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"3795b679-c38a-4fae-88f4-7a3498c5b08e\"><strong>Validez del Reembolso</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"acdafd4b-0796-45f5-829b-9b210e7b0d78\">30 días</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"263\"><p data-block-id=\"d1760170-fa28-4c8b-b533-419100be3192\"><strong>Integración compatible</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"286\"><p data-block-id=\"mf2fm6ny-gbpywt-002\"><a href=\"https://archive.developers.xendit.co/api-reference/#paylater\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Legacy API</a></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"2b081c08-ffd2-493a-b253-c4931f5f1c75\">Flujo de Pago</h2><p data-block-id=\"bb11ffcc-2536-43ef-8b4c-c1b92c023cd0\"><img data-block-id=\"eddfd494-8068-44bf-9d76-cc6fad49b419\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/ENG_-_Indodana_flow_a3kk0w.webp\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"713\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:713px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"acd97665-43b1-498b-89ca-e66b24c0a68f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"490a489a-2a58-4dc9-96ea-9e5cc09fc8be\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Indodana PayLater","Description":null}]